title: SaturdayÂ
content: Having seen my middle daughter off on her recce of south coast and far west universities l quickly got some shopping and hurried home to listen to Test Match Special. Rain had stopped play but the conversation was as interesting as ever. Pottered pleasantly in the garden as well as working on the above landship. Off on Monday as it is a holiday weekend in Fife.
